{"tid":727520,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"本田圭佑宣佈退出國家隊","createTime":"2018-07-03T05:48:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T11:53:35.000Z","uid":187076,"like":67,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"6d73deb1f0cbec6cae7f74c2f42b45787f80228c","tid":727520,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T05:48:35.000Z","msg":"日本於今屆世界盃打起了乾貴士、大迫勇也及柴崎岳等球員，作為3屆決賽周成員的老大哥本田圭佑，於球隊不敵比利時16強出局後宣布退出國家隊。<br />\n<br />\n今夜日本對比利時的16強一戰，肯定是俄羅斯世界盃其中最難忘一戰，日本隊於90分鐘內都沒有一刻放棄贏波，甚至補時階段獲得遠程罰球，處理的本田圭佑抱着入球的決心，30多碼一記強力的無旋射球僅僅被高圖爾斯撲出。<br />\n<br />\n全隊都不想進入加時，希望在法定時間贏波晉級，這便是本田的劇本，可惜卻是個令人傷感的結局，日本最終沒有創造奇蹟，再一次於16強止步。<br />\n<br />\n賽後本田亦宣布退出國家隊：「這便是現實，這就是世界盃，亦是我最後一屆世界盃。老實說我想帶領大家再晉一級，但現實卻是如此難受。」於3屆世界盃都有入球的本田直指全隊已盡力：「我認為我們盡力了，比利時值得贏波，我甚至認為日本已踢出接近最好的表現。我要多謝一直支持我的朋友，我在相同比數下落場，遺憾地最後以輸波收場&hellip;&hellip;不過現在再說這些說話都沒用了。」<br />\n<br />\nHK01全城足球狂熱專頁　完整賽程<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/134822_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F134822_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=dfa18e29&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b31ca4cc127d07e1f75e7bc213232ac27961b377","tid":727520,"uid":58958,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T05:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe4fc061ed90b4a847a6a5a11d9a483a5ff8382b","tid":727520,"uid":146435,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T08:15:46.000Z","msg":"日本隊識入波果個就係佢"},{"pid":"fa89d6be3e8fc7b5c2f4f73357b2dc231037da4f","tid":727520,"uid":13929,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T08:22:18.000Z","msg":"佢最後果個罰球真係好精彩"},{"pid":"c95757dcdeaeabeb55ea9ee1efad8c9e380690ba","tid":727520,"uid":6833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T08:43:52.000Z","msg":"本田<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2658f0fa027b3d6767e0a261b69743e3a7882552","tid":727520,"uid":2545,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"fa89d6be3e8fc7b5c2f4f73357b2dc231037da4f","tid":727520,"uid":13929,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T08:22:18.000Z","msg":"佢最後果個罰球真係好精彩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T08:46:20.000Z","msg":"衝力射球咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果射高少少可能都撲唔到"},{"pid":"775817c7e2ed9de2befa35d844af1a97f236d830","tid":727520,"uid":140599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T08:48:08.000Z","msg":"Honda.."},{"pid":"f1009dccb04de4a01e0ee14019f4d45d0ba93584","tid":727520,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T08:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ae40c5b59ae680b4c695289cd903a8dc818f14","tid":727520,"uid":34934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T08:54:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86902bc060a3f3917bd87f71804b3604ddb7b2f","tid":727520,"uid":186784,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2658f0fa027b3d6767e0a261b69743e3a7882552","tid":727520,"uid":2545,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"fa89d6be3e8fc7b5c2f4f73357b2dc231037da4f","tid":727520,"uid":13929,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T08:22:18.000Z","msg":"佢最後果個罰球真係好精彩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T08:46:20.000Z","msg":"衝力射球咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果射高少少可能都撲唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T08:55:55.000Z","msg":"佢罰球出左名係落葉式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkg